<br>
Frankly, I think the Founding Fathers, if they saw the state of the union today, would be spinning when they saw what lines Bush and co. were erasing....<br>
<br>
That would be much more in keeping with their intent, even from the Christian ones who wisely saw, as they werw pretty fresh from religious persecution, the merit in a secular government.<br>
