Where did you find the Jefferson quotes? Jefferson was not a Christian (he was Unitarian/Deist), and did not believe in a G-d who could have any kind of actions over the lives of men. He even wrote an alternative Bible, that left out the unsubstantiated stuff, and the supernatural stuff. Quite a different book, when he got done with it. He believed that if there was a G-d of some sort, he walked away from the affairs of man long ago.<br>
