Here's a good page for Jefferson:<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://www.nobeliefs.com/jefferson.htm">www.nobeliefs.com/jefferson.htm</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
