<br>
As a LDS of course I would have been personally offended if my governor choose to spew hate messages about my faith, but that is a different issue altogether.  I do not have the right to &quot;never be offended&quot;  Those hate messages had nothing to do with him exercising his own religion.  The two are not related.<br>
